snippet.title: Soul Hackers 2 — Announce Trailer | PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PC
snippet.description:
In a war between devil summoners, it's up to Ringo and her team to decrypt destiny and save the world from apocalypse! 

Soul Hackers 2 releases August 26, 2022 for Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Windows 10/11, and Steam!
